data.description: Nice renovated Single home  detached  located on a quiet street in sought after Palm Beach Leisureville.   Quartz kitchen counter. Vinyl water proof floors. Modern waterproof vinyl flooring throughout the social area and there is no carpet anywhere. The house is located close to many amenities  available for residents and guests, including 3 clubhouses with heated pools, well-equipped fitness center and a 18 hole golf course complimentary to residents and their guests.  Excellent location, only a few minutes from the beach and lots of restaurants and shops. Easy to show! Low HOA !!
